fastmcp (3.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Update to upstream v3.4.2
  * Upstream split fastmcp into a thin "fastmcp" meta-package plus the
    real implementation in the fastmcp_slim/ workspace member; build
    python3-fastmcp from fastmcp_slim/ instead of the repository root
  * Add debian/patch-pyproject.py to statically pin version and flatten
    fastmcp_slim's base + mcp + client + server extras into one
    dependency list, replacing the previous root pyproject.toml sed patch
  * Add python3-pydantic-settings, python3-typing-extensions,
    python3-starlette, python3-joserfc, python3-python-multipart
    dependencies pulled in by the new upstream dependency set

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Tue, 30 Jun 2026 22:57:24 +0200

